      • setRemote

        public void setRemote(URI remote)
        Sets the remote property of this MapsTo object to the given one.

        Parameters:
        remote -
        Throws:
        SBOLValidationException - if the associated SBOLDocument is not compliant

        IllegalArgumentException - if the given remote argument is not found in the list of functional components that are owned by the ModuleDefinition instance that this MapsTo object's parent Module instance refers to.
